<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1912-05-17T17:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1912-05-17T17:00:00-05:00" n="1107" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1107">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 312.11/446.</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the <gloss type="to">American Ambassador</gloss></hi>.</head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1912-05-17T17:00:00-05:00">
                                    <hi rend="italic">May 17, 1912—5 p.m.</hi>
                                </date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>Inform all deserving Americans who may wish to return to the United
                            States and have no other means to do so that the <hi rend="italic">Buford</hi> will touch at Manzanillo on or about May 22, San Bias
                            May 23, and Mazatlan May 24. It is desired to give the trip northward as
                            great publicity as possible, and in time to inform all Americans who
                            need assistance and transportation.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Knox.</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>